                                <head><hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi></head>
                                <p>No minutes of this meeting have been found. The information set
                                    forth above is from the Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_658">p. 658</ref>. At the beginning of the
                                    tripartite meeting, <hi rend="italic">infra</hi>, <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> summarized what he
                                    had said at this meeting with <persName corresp="#p_II1">Inönü</persName>.</p>
